<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="習禪" xml:id="gsz0759b14shiJuFang"><lb
ed="T" n="0759b14"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0759b14"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000021654"><placeName>鄆州</placeName><placeName>安國院</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010177">巨方</persName>傳（<persName key="A010186">智封</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0759b15"/><persName key="A010177">釋巨方</persName>，姓<name>曹</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000027682">安陸</placeName>人也。弱齡幹節立身，從<lb
ed="T" n="0759b16"/>師稟業於州治<placeName key="PL000000027663">明福院</placeName><persName key="A010184">朗<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，而聽誦《法<lb
ed="T" n="0759b17"/>華》、《維摩》二經，功畢受具。講述南宗論數席，<lb
ed="T" n="0759b18"/>即拂衣而起。禪會必參。後造北宗<persName key="A009582">秀<roleName>公</roleName></persName>所，銳<lb
ed="T" n="0759b19"/>精稽考，一見默許之。<persName key="A009582">秀</persName>問曰：「白雲散處如<lb
ed="T" n="0759b20"/>何？」曰：「不昧也。」又問：「到此間後如何？」曰：「正<lb
ed="T" n="0759b21"/>見一枝生五葉。」<persName key="A009582">秀</persName>頷之。數載之間，入室<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1381"/>侍<lb
ed="T" n="0759b22"/>對，庶幾真道，罕有倫儗。乃辭，觀方至<placeName key="PL000000004113"><placeName>上黨</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0759b23"/><placeName>寒嶺</placeName></placeName>而居。積稔之間，學徒數百，求請無阻。凡<lb
ed="T" n="0759b24"/>所提唱：真妄同源<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1412"/>、遲速異劑、得心助道、在<lb
ed="T" n="0759b25"/>乎修治，大較如此。<placeName key="PL000000021665">鄆</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0759005"/>帥<anchor xml:id="end0759005"/><persName key="A010185">吳文渙</persName>侍中欽慕<lb
ed="T" n="0759b26"/>其風，遣使請歸府，建<placeName key="PL000000021654">安國院</placeName>。傳法化徒，<lb
ed="T" n="0759b27"/>尚祖風者不離于席，頓悟多矣。<persName key="A010185">鄆<roleName>帥</roleName></persName>問曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0759b28"/>「今日後如何？」答云：「地布金沙，人安寶剎。」<persName key="A010185">吳<lb
ed="T" n="0759b29"/><roleName>帥</roleName></persName>信伏。因茲一府軍民，咸加宗仰。<name>吳</name>氏家<pb ed="T" n="0759c" xml:id="T50.2061.0759c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0759c01"/>無少長，重若神明，檀施<ptr type="glossary" target="#g237"/>豐厚。<persName key="A010177">方</persName>後於<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺<lb
ed="T" n="0759c02"/>山</placeName>道化，涉二十餘載。入滅時告眾曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010177">吾</ref>齒<lb
ed="T" n="0759c03"/>盡於此矣。」言訖長逝，春秋八十一。以<date key="j19868591986859" when-iso="+0727-09-26"><name>開元</name><lb
ed="T" n="0759c04"/>十五年九月三日</date>，全身入塔云。次<placeName key="PL000000005181"><placeName>河中府</placeName><placeName>安<lb
ed="T" n="0759c05"/>國院</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010186">釋智封</persName>，姓<name>吳</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000045938">懷安</placeName>人也。中年學道，<lb
ed="T" n="0759c06"/>勵操謹躬，行頭陀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g357"/>之行，卯食之後，水漿不<lb
ed="T" n="0759c07"/>度齒焉。於本州<placeName key="PL000000045850">清靜寺</placeName><persName key="A010188">恒<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>下落髮受<lb
ed="T" n="0759c08"/>具，綜習《<anchor xml:id="beg0759006"/>唯<anchor xml:id="end0759006"/>識論》<ptr target="#n767"/>。或人所詰，責之以滯于<lb
ed="T" n="0759c09"/>名相，憤發<ptr target="#n939"/>罷講。遊行登<placeName key="PL000000026781">武當山</placeName>，見<persName key="A009582">秀<roleName>師</roleName></persName>會<lb
ed="T" n="0759c10"/>疑氷解泮，思養聖胎<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1413"/>。倏辭，出<placeName key="PL000000005169"><placeName>蒲津</placeName><placeName>安峯山</placeName></placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0759c11"/>禁足十年，木食<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1479"/>澗飲。屬州牧<persName key="A010190">衛文昇</persName>請歸城<lb
ed="T" n="0759c12"/>內，建<placeName key="PL000000005181">新安國院</placeName>居之。因茲奔走，毳衣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1417"/>蔚然<lb
ed="T" n="0759c13"/>繁盛。<ref type="person" target="#A010190">使君</ref>問曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010190">某</ref>今日後如何？」對曰：「日從<lb
ed="T" n="0759c14"/>濛氾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1414"/>出，照樹全無影。」<ref type="person" target="#A010190">使君</ref>初不喻旨，拱<anchor xml:id="beg0759sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>葉</sic><corr>揖</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0759sgsz1"/><lb
ed="T" n="0759c15"/>而退。少選<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g654"/>開曉<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1415"/>，充詘<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1416"/>于懷。<persName key="A010186">封</persName>來往<placeName key="PL000000005168">中條山</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0759c16"/>二十餘年，儉薄不充。得其道者不可勝紀。<lb
ed="T" n="0759c17"/>入滅後，門人於州北三十步<ptr target="#n1371"/>建塔焉。</p>
